{"type":"text","timestamp":1778978947933,"sessionID":"ses_1cc98a909ffeIq1kBiDEN68vNf","part":{"id":"prt_e336870070017rUfNgxaA1CdoS","messageID":"msg_e33685751001xuzJSDXL1B4gd2","sessionID":"ses_1cc98a909ffeIq1kBiDEN68vNf","type":"text","text":"The nearest comparable terms mostly use `Wikipedia:` or `BIRNLEX:` definition xrefs, so I’m checking the local pattern for issue tracking and deciding whether to cite existing ontology sources or add a stronger publication-backed definition.","time":{"start":1778978942983,"end":1778978947931}}}
